schools.name: Pioneer Magnet School for the Visual and Performing Arts

data.description: This beautiful property near Tiger Creek Reservoir in Pioneer has space for the whole family and all of your toys! The five bedroom and two bathroom home has airbnb potential with a separate kitchenette and two bedrooms with a bathroom downstairs. Property has a 35x30 shop with a 30x14 loft, as well as RV parking and hookups with a circular driveway for easy access. Inside, the kitchen features hickory cabinets and beautiful countertops. Beautiful views from the large deck.
